{
  "stem": "16790.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I may have said hi, but that's about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We never had another discussion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was just, to me, it was just ironic that here this guy was, selling soda.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was a colonel in the Waffen-SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I got overseas, they were still doing denazification.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, that's sort of a weeding out process.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would-- they would bring people to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first thing I'd do was make them strip to the waist and check their left armpit-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tattoos, left armpit blood types, SS.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyone who had that, we sent them to Frankfurt for further interrogation and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was the-- in the preliminaries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was at the very beginning, you know, the first echelon, if you will, of weeding out people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those that were not in the SS, we checked the, the files to see if they were members of the party, the, the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if they were, find out exactly what their role was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In most cases, they just joined just to preserve their job and that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't-- once in a while, we came across some SS men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The town where I was was did have a concentration camp, slave labor camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were mostly Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were still there when we got there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was now a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so that became under my jurisdiction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I not only was a linguist, but I was also part of the military government.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to, more or less, maintain it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I really didn't have that much to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
